statements: SELECT * FROM printable_designs;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM printable_designs WHERE download_count > 100;
SELECT design_name, upload_date FROM printable_designs ORDER BY upload_date DESC;
SELECT designer_name, COUNT(design_id) AS total_designs FROM printable_designs GROUP BY designer_name;
SELECT * FROM printable_designs WHERE design_name LIKE 'S%' ORDER BY designer_name ASC;
SELECT design_id, design_name, designer_name, upload_date, download_count FROM printable_designs WHERE designer_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM printable_designs WHERE upload_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY designer_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM printable_designs WHERE download_count > 100 ORDER BY upload_date ASC;
SELECT design_name, designer_name, COUNT(*) AS total_designs FROM printable_designs GROUP BY designer_name HAVING total_designs > 1;
SELECT AVG(download_count) AS avg_downloads FROM printable_designs;
SELECT * FROM designs;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM designs WHERE design_id = 1;
SELECT designer_name, design_name, uploaded_date FROM designs ORDER BY designer_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM comments WHERE commenter_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT comment_text, comment_date FROM comments WHERE design_id = 2 ORDER BY comment_date DESC;
SELECT design_name, designer_name, uploaded_date FROM designs WHERE design_name LIKE 'S%' ORDER BY uploaded_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT design_name, designer_name, uploaded_date FROM designs WHERE designer_name = 'John Doe' ORDER BY design_name ASC, uploaded_date DESC;

SELECT design_name, designer_name, comment_text, commenter_name, comment_date FROM designs INNER JOIN comments ON designs.design_id = comments.design_id WHERE designer_name = 'Jane Smith' ORDER BY comment_date ASC, design_id DESC;

SELECT design_name, designer_name, COUNT(comment_id) AS num_comments FROM designs LEFT JOIN comments ON designs.design_id = comments.design_id GROUP BY design_name, designer_name HAVING num_comments > 3 ORDER BY num_comments DESC, design_name ASC;
SELECT designer_name, COUNT(*) AS num_designs FROM designs GROUP BY designer_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY num_designs DESC, designer_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM printable_designs;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM printable_designs ORDER BY designer_name ASC;
SELECT design_name, description FROM printable_designs WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM printable_designs WHERE designer_name = 'John Smith';
SELECT design_name, designer_name, design_file_path FROM printable_designs ORDER BY design_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM printable_designs WHERE id = 1;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM printable_designs ORDER BY designer_name DESC;
SELECT design_name FROM printable_designs WHERE design_name LIKE '%pattern%';
SELECT * FROM print_stats WHERE print_duration > 60 AND material_used = 'PLA';
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM printable_designs INNER JOIN print_stats ON printable_designs.id = print_stats.print_id;
SELECT * FROM design_catalog;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM design_catalog;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM design_catalog WHERE design_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM design_printers WHERE printer_type = 'FDM';
SELECT design_name, designer_name, upload_date FROM design_catalog ORDER BY upload_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM design_catalog;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM design_catalog WHERE design_id = 1;
SELECT design_name, designer_name, upload_date FROM design_catalog WHERE designer_name = 'John Smith';
SELECT tag_name FROM design_tags WHERE tag_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT * FROM design_catalog ORDER BY upload_date DESC, design_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM designs;
SELECT design_name, designer_name FROM designs WHERE download_count > 100 ORDER BY upload_date DESC;
SELECT design_name, COUNT(*) AS tag_count FROM designs JOIN design_tags ON designs.design_id = design_tags.design_id GROUP BY design_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT designer_name, AVG(rating_value) AS avg_rating FROM designs JOIN ratings ON designs.design_id = ratings.design_id GROUP BY designer_name ORDER BY avg_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM designs WHERE upload_date > '2022-01-01' AND download_count < 50 ORDER BY design_name;
SELECT * FROM designs WHERE designer_name IS NOT NULL ORDER BY upload_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT design_name, designer_name, upload_date FROM designs WHERE download_count > 100 ORDER BY designer_name ASC;
SELECT d.design_name, t.tag_name FROM designs d JOIN design_tags dt ON d.design_id = dt.design_id JOIN tags t ON dt.tag_id = t.tag_id WHERE t.tag_name = 'Technology' ORDER BY d.design_name;
SELECT d.design_name, AVG(r.rating_value) AS average_rating FROM designs d LEFT JOIN ratings r ON d.design_id = r.design_id GROUP BY d.design_name ORDER BY average_rating DESC;
SELECT d.design_name, COUNT(c.comment_id) AS comment_count FROM designs d LEFT JOIN comments c ON d.design_id = c.design_id GROUP BY d.design_name ORDER BY comment_count DESC;
